    "body": "I think this may have something to do with #8086. \r\n\r\n@rauljordan What do you think? \r\n\r\nI think we should be using RPC [ethereum.v1.Slasher.IsSlashableAttestationNoUpdate](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/9d737d60f4030e5fa68c3272b2285e61af6dd236/proto/slashing/slashing.proto#L23) but we are actually using [ethereum.v1.Slasher.IsSlashableAttestation](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/9d737d60f4030e5fa68c3272b2285e61af6dd236/proto/slashing/slashing.proto#L16) which requires a signature.",
